				"string" : "## Core Design Commitments (as stated)\n\nSmalltalk is presented not as a single technology but as a **coherent system** integrating:\n\n* a *language of description* (programming language),\n* a *language of interaction* (user interface),\n* an object-oriented storage model,\n* a message-oriented processing model,\n* and a virtual machine designed to support these uniformly.\n\nThe article insists that no part of the system should be exempt from these principles.\n"
